title: Tex-Mex Tofu & Roast Veggie Buddha Bowl with Charred Corn & Plant-Based Mayo
description: There’s so much to choose from, where should we start! The veggies looks so vibrant, but the barbecue and Tex-Mex glaze on the tofu is making everyone’s mouth water. Perhaps we should begin with the refreshing charred corn slaw? There’s too much choice, so let’s have it all!

